deprivation.

316
00:16:19,945 --> 00:16:22,280
We now begin a fast
that will continue

317
00:16:22,316 --> 00:16:24,115
until the day of the wedding.

318
00:16:24,154 --> 00:16:25,919
Well, th-that's four days away.

319
00:16:25,958 --> 00:16:27,450
It is a short time

320
00:16:27,494 --> 00:16:29,795
I know, but we must
make the best of it.

321
00:16:29,832 --> 00:16:32,999
What are
the other five trials?

322
00:16:33,039 --> 00:16:36,376
Blood, pain, sacrifice,
anguish...

323
00:16:36,413 --> 00:16:37,780
and death.

324
00:16:37,817 --> 00:16:39,480
