Grandma?

354
00:17:44,597 --> 00:17:45,930
Guess again.

355
00:17:49,608 --> 00:17:50,907
We're still on the?

356
00:17:50,944 --> 00:17:55,181
The road to <i>Kal'Hyah,</i> day 500.

357
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:57,281
Maybe we should
turn down the heat

358
00:17:57,324 --> 00:17:59,260
