359
00:17:59,296 --> 00:18:00,423
Oh, no, it's okay.

360
00:18:00,465 --> 00:18:01,455
I, uh...

361
00:18:01,500 --> 00:18:04,496
I just need some water.

362
00:18:04,541 --> 00:18:07,308
Now, you don't want
to push yourself too hard.

363
00:18:07,346 --> 00:18:10,649
You know, turning down the heat
might be a good idea.

364
00:18:11,924 --> 00:18:14,259
The whole point is
to push yourself

365
00:18:14,296 --> 00:18:16,494
to the limits of your endurance.

366
00:18:21,946 --> 00:18:23,175
I will.

367
00:18:23,215 --> 00:18:26,814
I want to travel
the entire path to <i>Kal'Hyah.</i>

368
00:18:26,857 --> 00:18:28,588
Stoke the fire again!

369
00:18:28,627 --> 00:18:30,597
