406
00:20:10,884 --> 00:20:12,820
At best, you'd be
an object of pity

407
00:20:12,856 --> 00:20:16,854
but you'd never be accepted,
never an equal

408
00:20:16,932 --> 00:20:20,269
because you can never
truly be one of us.

409
00:20:26,987 --> 00:20:29,891
<i>Ko'ma tlang'goS ak-bay</i>

410
