423
00:21:15,727 --> 00:21:17,287
Am I?

424
00:21:18,701 --> 00:21:21,868
Your task is to recite
the complete chronicle

425
00:21:21,907 --> 00:21:24,378
of the women in my family.

426
00:21:24,412 --> 00:21:26,041
I just thought I'd give you

427
00:21:26,083 --> 00:21:28,919
a broader historical perspective
along the way.

428
00:21:28,956 --> 00:21:32,157
I am familiar
with Klingon history.

429
00:21:32,197 --> 00:21:37,539
Now, return to the story
of my 23rd maternal grandmother

430
00:21:37,575 --> 00:21:40,776
Shenara,
daughter of Emperor Reclaw

431
00:21:40,815 --> 00:21:42,911
in the Second Dynasty.

432
00:21:42,954 --> 00:21:46,759
Well, that's where we run
into a little bit of a problem.

433
00:21:46,795 --> 00:21:48,697
You see, I did some research

434
00:21:48,733 --> 00:21:50,966
and when Emperor Reclaw
was killed

435
00:21:51,004 --> 00:21:53,703
all of the members
of the Imperial Family

436
00:21:53,744 --> 00:21:56,215
were put to death,
including Shenara.

437
00:21:56,250 --> 00:21:59,519
When the Third Dynasty
was founded ten years later

438
00:21:59,557 --> 00:22:02,724
a new group of Klingons
were given the titles

439
00:22:02,763 --> 00:22:05,930
