Imperial blood in your veins

451
00:22:38,743 --> 00:22:41,875
and that's exactly what we'll
keep telling everyone.

452
00:22:45,391 --> 00:22:48,511
Continue with the saga.

453
00:22:48,643 --> 00:22:51,114
My pleasure.

454
00:22:53,154 --> 00:22:54,315
Hey, Major.

455
00:22:54,356 --> 00:22:56,121
