a party tomorrow night?

456
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,561
Ah, news travels fast.

457
00:22:57,597 --> 00:22:59,066
Well, is it by invitation or?

458
00:22:59,100 --> 00:23:00,159
I'm sure you're welcome.

459
00:23:00,202 --> 00:23:02,172
And you can tell Nog
the same goes for him, too.

460
00:23:02,207 --> 00:23:03,175
Great.

461
00:23:03,209 --> 00:23:05,179
Oh, I understand
congratulations are in order

462
00:23:05,213 --> 00:23:06,580
to our newest published author.

463
00:23:06,617 --> 00:23:07,744
Thank you.

464
00:23:12,396 --> 00:23:13,729
What was all that about?

465
00:23:13,766 --> 00:23:14,734
Nothing.

466
00:23:14,768 --> 00:23:16,032
There they go.

467
00:23:18,075 --> 00:23:19,942
They look so serious.

468
00:23:19,979 --> 00:23:21,278
It's all an act.

469
00:23:21,316 --> 00:23:22,945
